snippet.title: Breached Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: The game is about data stalking, drone flights and resource scavenging set in the year 2245. After being awakened from hibernation you discover a desert covered world. With you shelter damaged and a minimal supply of oxygen, you have to explore the desert and rebuild your shelter.
